formal campaigning began today for next months 
general elections but the contest has been overshadowed by a 
public exchange between the only leader singapore has known and his 
designated successor 
the tension began in a threehour speech aug 14 when prime 
minister lee kuan yew cited the shortcomings of deputy prime 
minister goh chok tong on monday he suggested goh see a 
