lee said monday that his deputy could not communicate as well on 
television and at mass meetings as he could in small groups i 
dont know why i have suggested to him perhaps a bit of 
psychological adjustment maybe a psychiatrist something holds him 
back 
goh told reporters tuesday that lee suggested he consult a 
psychologist not a psychiatrist who is for mentally distressed 
people 
i do not believe that a psychologist could help me a speech 
therapist and trainer will and i have been seeing my speech 
