using the gasses is based on environmental samples taken from the 
angolan battle zone in april 
janes defense weekly is an authoritative publication dealing 
with military matters worldwide 
soil leaf and water samples showed clear traces of mustard gas 
and nerve gases heyndrickx was quoted as saying 
the attack must have taken place in march or april heyndrickx 
